、Prompt、RAG、Agent、Eval 的分工，避免把不同问题混为一谈。</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"prototype-card\">\n          <div class=\"concept-tabs\" role=\"tablist\" aria-label=\"AI 核心概念\">\n            <button class=\"active\" type=\"button\" data-concept=\"llm\">LLM</button>\n            <button type=\"button\" data-concept=\"prompt\" class=\"\">Prompt</button>\n            <button type=\"button\" data-concept=\"rag\" class=\"\">RAG</button>\n            <button type=\"button\" data-concept=\"agent\" class=\"\">Agent</button>\n            <button type=\"button\" data-concept=\"eval\" class=\"\">Eval</button>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"concept-feature\">\n            <div class=\"video-placeholder\">\n              <button class=\"video-play\" type=\"button\" aria-label=\"播放核心概念介绍\">▶</button>\n              <div class=\"video-bar\"><strong>▶</strong><span></span><small>01:32 / 04:20</small></div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"concept-copy\">\n              <h2 id=\"conceptTitle\">LLM</h2>\n              <p id=\"conceptIntro\">大语言模型，擅长理解、生成、总结、推理，但会犯错，也不天然懂业务。123</p>\n              <div class=\"concept-point\">\n                <span class=\"concept-icon\" id=\"conceptIconOne\">好</span>\n                <div><h3 id=\"conceptPointTitleOne\">它擅长什么</h3><p id=\"conceptPointTextOne\">理解文本、生成内容、信息提炼、基础推理。</p></div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"concept-point\">\n                <span class=\"concept-icon\" id=\"conceptIconTwo\">限</span>\n                <div><h3 id=\"conceptPointTitleTwo\">它不擅长什么</h3><p id=\"conceptPointTextTwo\">天然掌握企业知识、稳定执行复杂流程、自动保证正确。</p></div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"concept-point\">\n                <span class=\"concept-icon\" id=\"conceptIconThree\">想</span>\n                <div><h3 id=\"conceptPointTitleThree\">你该如何理解</h3><p id=\"conceptPointTextThree\">LLM 是能力底座，不等于完整解决方案。</p></div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </section>\n     